Hi Jordan! My name is Judy Edwards. I'm really excited to get more information about your school.

Perfect! Judy, let me assure you that your information is secure with us. We take data security very seriously at Harmony Music School.

That's great to hear, Jordan! I'm really excited to start lessons soon.

We're thrilled to have you join us, Judy! If you need anything else, feel free to reach out. Thank you for your time today!

Thank you, Jordan! I look forward to it.

Have a wonderful day, Judy!
